data.description:
Do You love Mountain Cabins but Can't move to the Mountains? I have the Home for You!  This Home has wood walls as u walk in and continues through the hall. Gives You a Mountain Cabin feeling. The Home has New paint on the outside and inside. This home has New flooring in the Den, dining room, Hall, Kitchen and Bathrooms. It has a brand new Hot Water heater. This Home has had updates but still needs some more updating to it. It has 3 bed rooms and 2 baths. Off the kitchen is a bonus room that has heat and air with a walk in closet. The Garage has been enclosed.
This Home has a Gas fireplace. The Kitchen over looks a beautiful backyard and the storage shed stays. All Appliances Stay except for freezer in the Laundry room. This home is located near all the shops and restaurants. This home is in the Brookwood school District. 
For Showings Please send Text!
We will be doing showings everyday After 2pm and showings end at 7pm by appt. Only! This home is Occupied.
This home is located in a very quiet neighborhood. Owner is not going to do anymore updates to this home what is left to be done is up to the New Buyer to make their Own Style. We love this home and hope You will too!
This is not a home for investors. The owner is not interested in lease purchases. The Owner will pay up to 3% buyer fee. Only serious buyers wanted. Thanks!
data.whatILove: We love Our Home's location and Our wood walls in our Den and Dining Room and down our hall! We love how it looks like a Cabin!
